comments: During the rebound, Mann (LAC) grabs Clarke's (MEM) jersey and impedes his ability to retrieve the rebound.
George (LAC) steps out of bounds as he attempts to retrieve the rebound.
During the drive, Bledsoe (LAC) legally contests Melton's (MEM) shot attempt, and makes marginal contact with his off arm near the rim.
Contact between Mann (LAC) and Clarke (MEM) during the rebound is marginal.
Clarke (MEM) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to Los Angeles.
Jackson (LAC) makes marginal contact with Bane's (MEM) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
George (LAC) hooks Melton (MEM) during the drive to the basket.
Clarke (MEM) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by George (LAC).
As Clarke (MEM) jumps from the backcourt, he establishes frontcourt position with his right foot prior to receiving the pass.
Bledsoe (LAC) avoids making contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) extends his off-arm outwards but the contact with Bledsoe (LAC) is marginal.
Melton (MEM) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Kennard (LAC) commits a take foul on Bane (MEM).
Melton (MEM) makes contact to the arm of George (LAC) in transition but the contact is marginal.
Melton (MEM) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the jump shot attempt by George (LAC).
